<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<< Rulare >>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
    Pentru crearea biblioteci:
    *) make build


    Pentru eliminare executabil:
    *) make clean
